title: IAA Tonight | Brady and the Bucs Continue to Struggle AND Russell Westbrook Off the Bench?
description: Tom Brady and the Tampa Bay Buccaneers continue to struggle after falling to the Baltimore Ravens 27-22 on Thursday Night Football. Could Tom's personal life be affecting his play, or is the team just overall bad and won't be able to compete in the NFC? Plus, Russell Westbrook will be coming off the bench for the forseeable future. Is this the correct move for the Lakers to be making?
author: smanderville@houseofathlete.com (Leger Douzable, Chantel Tremetiere, Omar Kelly)
